  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">User Generated Content and Public Activities Including Comments We offer you the opportunity to engage in public activities on our Web Sites and other SIDEARM Services Public activities include any actions you take on our Web Sites that are designed to be visible to other users including comments or any other items that you submit Any information you disclose in your public activities along with your screen name or ID or any image or photo becomes public and may be used by SIDEARM Sports for online and offline promotional or commercial uses in any and all media If you choose to engage in public activities you should be aware that any personal information you submit can be read collected and used by other users We are not responsible for the personally identifiable information you choose to submit in the course of your public activities and we have no responsibility to publish take down remove or edit any of your public activities or submissions</evidence>
